                                                           "The frequency at which the Dataset is updated (DCAT-AP 3.0)."@en ;
                                              rdfs:label "accrual periodicity"@en ,
                                                         "periodicidad de actualización"@es .


###  http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty .


###  http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator
<http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
                                   rdfs:range <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/Agent> ;
                                   rdfs:comment "An entity responsible for making the resource (DCAT-AP 3.0 / DCTERMS)."@en ,
                                                "Una entidad responsable de crear el recurso (DCAT-AP 3.0 / DCTERMS)."@es ;
                                   rdfs:label "creador"@es ,
                                              "creator"@en .


###  http://purl.org/dc/terms/format
